  "description": "Non-material amendment to planning permission ref: 2018/02580/FUL of which appeal ref: APP/H5390/W/18/3218226 granted 28th May 2019 for the 'Erection of front and rear roof extensions following the removal of existing rear roof extensions at no. 11 and 13 Peterborough Road; erection of rear roof extension over the back addition of no.11 at second floor level; removal of external chimney stacks between no. 11 and 13 Peterborough Road; installation of new rooflights in the front roofslopes and above the main flat roof at roof level; conversion of existing flat at first floor level of no. 11 Peterborough Road and second floor level of no. 11 and 13 Peterborough Road into 1 x 1 and 1 x 2 bedroom self-contained flats.' Amendments to include: Re-positioning of 2no approved rooflights in the front roofslope, addition of 2no rooflights above the main flat roof at roof level, reduction of the rear mansard roof's approved height, removal of the approved dormer window and installation of 2no rooflights in the rear roofslope, re-positioning of 2no approved French windows with Juliet balconies in the rear roofslope and to the rear of second floor back addition, retention of the existing chimney stacks, internal alterations to second floor level to change from 1 x 2 bedroom flat into 1 x 3 bedroom flat by the introduction of a new entrance at first floor level, re-position of the main staircase leading to the main entrances of the first floor 1 x 1 bed flat and second floor 1 x 3 bed duplex flat.",
